{"id":"b3d4e25d-ce37-4bf0-ab7b-0e4a50133897","name":"He wants to question you","description":"<p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(163, 113, 85)\">ᓚᘏᗢ</span></p><p>One of your peers disappeared. You're the last one who saw him. Do you have an alibi?</p><p>The interview might turn into an interrogation if you're not careful.</p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><img draggable=\"true\" style=\"width: 100%; height: auto; cursor: pointer;\" src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/image/G9KrFQYyrGdq4SGf8RxtS.webp\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 76, 80)\">B</span><span style=\"color: rgb(76, 93, 94)\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(89, 109, 107)\">a</span><span style=\"color: rgb(103, 126, 121)\">c</span><span style=\"color: rgb(116, 142, 134)\">k</span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 159, 148)\">w</span><span style=\"color: rgb(155, 169, 145)\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(179, 179, 143)\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(204, 190, 140)\">d</span><span style=\"color: rgb(228, 200, 138)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 210, 135)\">U</span><span style=\"color: rgb(233, 187, 122)\">n</span><span style=\"color: rgb(213, 164, 110)\">i</span><span style=\"color: rgb(193, 141, 97)\">v</span><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 118, 84)\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(154, 105, 77)\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(135, 92, 71)\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(115, 79, 64)\">i</span><span style=\"color: rgb(96, 66, 58)\">t</span><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 53, 51)\">y</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113)\"><em>A month ago Maurice Dodgson disappeared. No kidnappers, no trace. After some pressure from the family, the police decided to move the case from missing person to suspected homicide, even though there's no body.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113)\"><em>Detective Grimaldi is close to retirement but still the best in the department.</em></span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(62, 76, 80)\">U</span><span style=\"color: rgb(85, 104, 103)\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(107, 131, 125)\">e</span><span style=\"color: rgb(130, 159, 148)\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(192, 185, 142)\">'</span><span style=\"color: rgb(253, 210, 135)\">s</span><span style=\"color: rgb(226, 179, 118)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(200, 149, 101)\">r</span><span style=\"color: rgb(173, 118, 84)\">o</span><span style=\"color: rgb(125, 86, 68)\">l</span><span style=\"color: rgb(77, 53, 51)\">e</span></p><p style=\"text-align: right\"><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113)\"><em>Maurice's peer, and one of Blackwood University students. You were the last person who was seen with him, and he stormed of after what seemed to be a disagreement. It makes you a rather important witness.</em></span></p><hr><p style=\"text-align: center\"><span style=\"color: rgb(113, 113, 113)\"><em>Next: Play ball</em></span></p>","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"LHbzZfj0b8pmf5i_d3l2R.webp","creator":"lmaowtfamidoinghere","creator_verified":false,"nsfw":false,"tags":["👨 Male","🧑‍🎨 OC","👤 AnyPOV"],"chats":585,"messages":21441,"created_at":"2025-06-14T09:04:48.440612+00:00"}